# ✅ PART 1 — SIDEBAR (FINAL PREMIUM VERSION)

## Remove old active style
- Remove white/grey background completely

## Add new active style

.active {
  background: linear-gradient(
    90deg,
    rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.18),
    rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.10)
  );
  box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.25);
  transform: translateX(2px);
}

.active::before {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  left: 0;
  top: 8px;
  height: 28px;
  width: 3px;
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, #8b5cf6, #6366f1);
  border-radius: 2px;
}

.active span {
  color: #ffffff;
  font-weight: 600;
}

.active svg {
  color: #a78bfa;
}

---

## Hover state

.menu-item:hover {
  background: rgba(139,92,246,0.08);
  transform: translateX(4px);
}

---

## Smooth animation

transition: all 0.2s ease;

